@page "/privacy"

<PageTitle>Privacy Policy - VoronoiGen</PageTitle>
<HeadContent>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow" />
</HeadContent>

<main style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 16px 60px; line-height:1.7; font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: November 5, 2025</em></p>

    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>VoronoiGen is a free, client-side tool. We do not collect, store, or transmit your files to any server. All processing happens in your browser.</p>

    <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Files:</strong> Your uploaded DXF files are processed entirely in your browser and never leave your device.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use cookies to remember your consent preferences for advertising.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics (Optional):</strong> If enabled, Google Analytics collects anonymous usage data.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google may use cookies to serve ads based on your interests. You can opt out at any time.</p>
    <p>Learn more: <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads">Google Ads Policy</a></p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You can reject cookies at any time using the consent banner. Your files are never uploaded to our servers.</p>

    <p><a href="/" style="color:#4af;">← Back to Tool</a></p>
</main>

<footer style="max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto 40px; padding:0 16px; color:#666; font-size:0.95rem;">
    <hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #eee; margin:0 0 16px;" />
    <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px;">
        <span>&copy; @DateTime.Now.Year VoronoiGen</span>
        <span><a href="/privacy" style="color:#3366cc; text-decoration:none;">Privacy</a></span>
    </div>
</footer>
